{"tid":1686180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[大灣區榮耀]操刀 DQ 黃之鋒　選舉主任蔡亮西貢住所被疑僭建","createTime":"2019-11-01T03:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T06:33:53.000Z","uid":22453,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8d94b2b8277c634f3aded5f5e392a35ddea86e","tid":1686180,"uid":22453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:29:43.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒早前報名南區「海怡西」選區區議會選舉，最終被裁定提名無效，而負責「DQ」黃之鋒的南區選舉主任蔡亮，被指知法犯法，《蘋果日報》報道，蔡亮在位於西貢柏濤軒的獨立屋住所懷疑有僭建物。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》指，蔡亮住所的懷疑僭建物築在天台，天台上面有一間 300 呎的玻璃屋。除此之外，住所門外亦有一塊長約 5 米的透明玻璃簷篷，同樣疑屬僭建。<br />\n<br />\n1994 年加入政府的蔡亮，在 2014 年 8 月起出任油尖旺民政事務專員。黃之鋒宣布參選之後，南區選舉主任馬周佩芬負責處理黃之鋒的參選提名，但直至提名期結束，黃之鋒都未獲得結果，到了 10 月 24 日，政府指馬周佩芬「因病休假」，由蔡亮兼任南區選舉主任。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒最終在 10 月 29 日收到蔡亮的信件回覆，指他提名無效。蔡亮回覆黃之鋒的信件提到，黃之鋒曾在回覆選舉主任的信件引述國家主席習近平說「搞國家分裂只會粉身碎骨」，令黃之鋒不提倡或支持港獨是自決選項，這情況反映黃之鋒是因為受「嚴詞威脅」才妥協。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醬汁：<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%93%8D%E5%88%80-dq-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E8%94%A1%E4%BA%AE%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E8%A2%AB%E7%96%91%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%2588%2580-dq-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2594%25A1%25E4%25BA%25AE%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2583%25AD%25E5%25BB%25BA%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=0f6596da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%2588%2580-dq-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2594%25A1%25E4%25BA%25AE%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2583%25AD%25E5%25BB%25BA%2F&h=840ee7fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%93%8D%E5%88%80-dq-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E8%94%A1%E4%BA%AE%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E8%A2%AB%E7%96%91%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"c63d67fab4824f343f0df0f2c4401f1149301c5a","tid":1686180,"uid":38317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"甴近平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850597bffebcb2c8233c0506b7b44d6274436f5c","tid":1686180,"uid":22453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得要住安全屋<br />\n原來間屋唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf173e1d16773866f42e76642b50f8bdeb2c9357","tid":1686180,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"你還有黨 返大灣區住 起夠廿個都冇人理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be35286394dc44e1e1ee8d9f65103de3645f34b","tid":1686180,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"蘋果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6041618fdbd5180f545e94f9eadbef3a9cde25a3","tid":1686180,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721,831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /